00:05:54.680 --> 00:05:58.250
-wing worldview well it could be either we don't know

00:05:58.280 --> 00:06:00.670
just by the fact that it's popular we don't know

00:06:00.670 --> 00:06:04.860
why people upvoted it but the community notes algorithm breaks

00:06:04.860 --> 00:06:07.600
